You are a senior frontend engineer reviewing a pull request for a Raycast UI clone project. The task is THEME002 - "Add compact mode" with these requirements:

- When no query is entered, show only the search bar (hide list and action panel)
- List appears with fade-in when user starts typing
- Revert to compact when query is cleared
- Toggle via prop on CommandPalette
- Animate height transition

Please review the following changes and identify any issues, bugs, or improvements needed:

### 1. command_palette.tsx changes:
Added `compact?: boolean` prop. When true, adds `command-palette--compact` CSS class.

### 2. command_palette.scss changes:
Added collapsible wrapper using CSS Grid row collapse trick:
```scss
.command-palette__collapsible {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-rows: 1fr;
  transition: grid-template-rows $transition-slow ease-out;

  .command-palette--compact & {
    grid-template-rows: 0fr;
  }
}

.command-palette__collapsible-inner {
  overflow: hidden;
  opacity: 1;
  transition: opacity $transition-normal ease-out;

  .command-palette--compact & {
    opacity: 0;
  }
}
```

### 3. App.tsx changes:
- Added `isCompact = viewType === 'root' && !query.trim()` computed value
- Pass `compact={isCompact}` to CommandPalette
- Wrapped body content + ActionPanel in `<div className="command-palette__collapsible"><div className="command-palette__collapsible-inner">...</div></div>`
- Overlays (QuickLook, Alert, Toast, HUD) are NOT inside the collapsible wrapper

Review specifically for:
1. CSS Grid `grid-template-rows: 0fr` browser compatibility
2. Whether the transition is smooth (opacity + grid-template-rows)
3. Whether the compact state logic is correct (only root view, no query)
4. Whether overlays are correctly excluded from collapsible
5. Any edge cases (e.g., user has query → navigates to pushed view → pops back, does compact re-engage?)
6. Accessibility concerns
7. Whether the collapsible wrapper could break existing flex layouts
8. Whether the `display: flex; flex-direction: column` on `.command-palette` plays well with the grid collapsible child

Read the actual files to verify:
- /Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/lol/src/components/command_palette/command_palette.tsx
- /Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/lol/src/components/command_palette/command_palette.scss
- /Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/lol/src/App.tsx

Provide a detailed review with any issues found.

